        "Calculate signal-to-noise ratio",
        "Estimate QBER contribution from noise",
        "Determine timing requirements",
        "Compare detector options"
      ],
      "expectedOutput": "Detection system comparison tool",
      "hints": [
        "SNSPDs have better performance but need cryo",
